n。。。。。。<br />\n包容性及言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n香港觀察網站"},{"pid":"c2a733f762e269d8cca619a1334f54b6176b5f5b","tid":2100284,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:59:15.000Z","msg":"肥彭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123790a71b0021a949a3f72a95077779f9ccf5e0","tid":2100284,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:00:14.000Z","msg":"彭彭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cc096488f0e38f48e09c3cbc9a0f4bbd9c1a25","tid":2100284,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />彭督好過任何一位主權移交後嘅話事人"},{"pid":"030e6ee864ba3aaa999d7150d2893b8c4dc0462a","tid":2100284,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:08:52.000Z","msg":"多謝人唔好得口講<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Watch 籌左幾日得1000個人捐左錢？續左BNO嘅人都唔止1000人啦。香港人唔該做返啲嘢啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2060703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2060703</a><br />\n樓主PIN pls"},{"pid":"a6daa10baabaece336ecc6b44961b1b4297e66a7","tid":2100284,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7cc096488f0e38f48e09c3cbc9a0f4bbd9c1a25","tid":2100284,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />彭督好過任何一位主權移交後嘅話事人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:13:45.000Z","msg":"根本無得比，拎得黎比既已經本質有問題"}]}